    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Zoe
    _sentences: 'Wha- Hey! That''s my sword!

      Give it back'
  - _profile: {fileID: 7694656284260392015, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
      type: 3}
    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Red Guy
    _sentences: 'Come take it then.

      Makes it much easier to take the rest.'
  - _profile: {fileID: 7983353289166243739, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
      type: 3}
    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Sparks
    _sentences: 'Zoe, make a tactical retreat into that sewer grate.

      Quickly
      before we lose the girl.'
  - _profile: {fileID: -1996703693659354134, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
      type: 3}
    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Zoe
    _sentences: 'But I, grrr.

      You better keep your head on a swivel next time
      jerk.'
